&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1"># 1. 精准计算张量形状（按字节级控制显存）&lt;/span>
