&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nb">print&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="sa">f&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;目标显存: &lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">args&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">mem_gb&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">GB | 实际占用: &lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">allocated_mem_gb&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">.4f&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">GB&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nb">print&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="sa">f&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;张量形状: &lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">shape&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2"> | 持续计算: &lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">args&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">duration&lt;/span>&lt;span class="si">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">秒&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">\n&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
